Evaluation Criteria

    Code Quality:
        Code is clean, well-structured, and contains meaningful comments.

    React Native Usage:
        Efficient use of components (e.g., View, Text, Image, Button, ScrollView) and navigation.

    Data Handling:
        API data is fetched asynchronously and displayed correctly.
        Handles loading, error scenarios, and state management.

    UI Design:
        The app has a simple and clean layout with proper spacing, fonts, and image alignment.
        Avatar is displayed as a rounded image.

    Error Handling:
        Error handling is in place for API calls, and edge cases such as navigation boundaries are managed.
